<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_92" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_92_r2l15"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hanſen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Roſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_92_r2l16"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her hans / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> Juden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l17"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Alſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> hawſfrawn des geligens beÿ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l18">vns durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_92_line_1571166010761_239"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab></add> günnen / . vnd ew des nicht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l19">wan vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb vnd <expan>freuntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweiſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l20"><expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria <expan>Sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r2l21"><expan>Palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> Anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_92" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
