<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hans, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> juden
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> hawsfrawn des geligens bey uns durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen
                                <add><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan></add> günnen und ew des nicht
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sage<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wan wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und
                            <expan>freuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria
                                <expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nicam</expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan> anno x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
